The paper presents a new algorithm for black-box variational inference, which is a common technique in machine learning and statistics. The paper focuses on optimization methods and convergence guarantees, which are typical topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), and control systems (cs.SY).
